    "• Prompts.csv: A CSV file that stores the prompts used in generating the dialogues by the ChatGPT model.",
    "These prompts provide instructions and guidelines for initiating conversations between the expert and user within the context of discussing artworks in a museum setting.",
    "• Dialogues.csv: A CSV file containing the actual dialogues generated by the ChatGPT model.",
    "Each dialogue entry consists of conversational turns between the expert and user agents.",
    "• Metrics.csv: A CSV file providing a summary of evaluation metrics obtained to assess the quality and characteristics of the generated dialogues."
